                               data-trigger="focus"
                               title="FUND FEE"
                               data-content="<div>This fee covers the cost of administration, and are usually included in the annual management charge. However, older pensions may have a separate policy fee.</div><br/><div><strong>Choose a value between 0-100%.</strong></div>"
